K. Hari Kumar













                    
                    K Hari Kumar (a.k.a John Harker) is the first Indian author to crack into Amazon Kindle's Top 75 Bestsellers List in Horror, and Top 20 Bestsellers List in British Themed Books. His fascination for the unknown is clearly depicted in his works. His first book 'When Strangers Meet..' is a No.1 Amazon India Bestselling Title.He's also a two time international award nominated photographer and currently is a screenwriter in Mumbai.
                

